<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000937/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The course will be based on individual assignments.
Evaluación continua:
Students will work on various case studies and write an essay to analyze the situations presented in these cases, providing financial solutions. Each essay will account for 50% of their final grade. They must achieve a score of at least 5 out of 10 for each essay. If they fail to pass any of these assessments, they will be suspended.
Evaluación sólo prueba final:
Students must attend an exam based on case studies, which will constitute 100% of their final grade. If they fail this exam, they will be suspended and will need to attend the extraordinary exam.
Evaluación convocatoria extraordinaria:
The extraordinary exam will account for 100% of their final grade. If they fail this exam, they will be suspended and will need to repeat the course."""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000937/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
        <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/103000937/2025-26/evaluation/trial2>,
